<p>Best regards,<br/>Investment Team</p>', NULL, false, false, false, NULL, 'TEMPLATES', NULL, '2026-01-17 12:14:47.566966', '2026-01-17 12:14:47.566967', 'ccf4c725-f18b-4621-ace1-cb2a29ba5936', 'ccf4c725-f18b-4621-ace1-cb2a29ba5936', false),
