<p>Following up on our recent conversation about your portfolio performance. I''ve attached the detailed analysis we discussed, including:</p>

<ul>
<li>Year-to-date performance attribution</li>
<li>Risk metrics and volatility analysis</li>
<li>Benchmark comparison</li>
<li>Recommendations for Q1</li>
</ul>

<p>Please review and let me know if you have any questions. I''m available for a call this week to discuss further.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br/>Portfolio Management Team</p>', NULL, false, false, false, NULL, 'TEMPLATES', NULL, '2026-01-17 12:14:47.566969', '2026-01-17 12:14:47.56697', 'ccf4c725-f18b-4621-ace1-cb2a29ba5936', 'ccf4c725-f18b-4621-ace1-cb2a29ba5936', false),
	('d7d8fde7-ddda-4052-95ed-17cf104d3cbe', '2779be28-889e-45eb-816b-98e9407dca9c', 'john@example.com', '', NULL, NULL, 'Investment Proposal: Growth Equity Strategy', '<p>Dear {name},</p>

<p>As discussed, I''m pleased to present our Growth Equity Strategy proposal. This strategy targets high-growth companies with strong fundamentals and sustainable competitive advantages.</p>

<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Target annual return: 15-20%</li>
<li>Diversified across 30-40 holdings</li>
<li>Focus on technology, healthcare, and consumer sectors</li>
<li>Active risk management with downside protection</li>
</ul>

<p>Minimum investment: $500,000<br/>
Management fee: 1.25% AUM<br/>
Performance fee: 15% above hurdle rate</p>

<p>Let me know if you''d like to schedule a detailed presentation.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br/>Investment Advisory Team</p>', NULL, false, false, false, NULL, 'TEMPLATES', NULL, '2026-01-17 12:14:47.566972', '2026-01-17 12:14:47.566972', 'ccf4c725-f18b-4621-ace1-cb2a29ba5936', 'ccf4c725-f18b-4621-ace1-cb2a29ba5936', false),
